title: Jens Waaben
text:
Jens is a Ph.D. Student at the university of Copenhagen supervised by Professor Søren Brunak. Jens’ research revovles around the Danish publich health registries and how we can use them to investigate sex-specific patterns in medication and diagnosis.



2023-2026: Ph.D. student at the University of Copenhagen
2020-2022: M.Sc. Bioinformatics and Systems biology, Technical University of Denmark
2015-2020: B.Sc. & M.Sc. Molecular biomedicine, University of Copenhagen
